  <summary date="2021-07-07T14:21:32Z" status="Introduced in House">Public Health Workforce Loan Repayment Act of 2021

This bill establishes a student loan repayment program for public health professionals. As a condition of participation, recipients must agree to complete a period of full-time employment with a state, tribal, or local public health agency.

Individuals eligible for this program include those with public health or health professions degrees, as well as those with degrees in statistics, computer science, or related information technology fields.</summary>
